getTrackingFactory

public static ValidationContextFactory getTrackingFactory(java.lang.Class<?> validationsIntf)
                                                   throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
Obtain a tracking ValidationContextFactory that supplies ValidationContext objects for the validations methods on the supplied validations interface.

A tracking ValidationContextFactory will only supply a ValidationContext for a particular validation method once. See ValidationContextFactory.get(String) for more information.

Parameters:
validationsIntf - The validator interface for which the factory will supply ValidationContext objects.
Returns:
A tracking ValidationContextFactory that supplies ValidationContext objects for the validation methods on the supplied interface.
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If there is an issue with the supplied validations interface - for example, if it contains overloaded methods.
